** [[VirtualBox]]: [[Download|download]] and [[Verify the virtual machine images|verify]] the {{project_name_long}} images before importing them.
** [[KVM]]: Follow the [[KVM#KVM_Setup_Instructions|KVM setup instructions]] to download, verify and import the {{project_name_long}} images. 
