In all cases, users should follow the [[Post Install Advice|Post-installation Security Advice]]. 

For greater security pre- and post-{{project_name_long}} installation, users should read the [[Documentation]] pages widely to learn more about potential threats and mitigations. For instance, users might like to consult the [[Design]] pages, and consider the recommendations outlined in the Basic Security Guide and Advanced Security Guide sections. Users with limited time can refer to the [[System_Hardening_Checklist|System Hardening Checklist]].

